title: Essential Avengers Vol. 3 (All-New Edition) (Trade Paperback)
description:
The Avengers have always represented strength through diversity. Among the ranks of Earth's Mightiest Heroes are Captain America, a hero out of time, thawed from an icy sleep since the end of World War II; Tony Stark, a.k.a. Iron Man, wealthy and privileged industrialist; the mighty Thor, Norse God of Thunder; and the Black Panther, warrior-born king of the African kingdom of Wakanda. But now, they have a new member of the team, unlike any that has come before... His name is the Vision and he represents the greatest diversity of all... for you see, he's an android! Collecting AVENGERS #47-68 and AVENGERS ANNUAL #2.
All Ages …$19.99
978-0-7851-0741-5
